com.yworks.yfiles.layout.multipage

Class LayoutContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.multipage.LayoutContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IElementInfoManager

    public class LayoutContext
extends Object
implements IElementInfoManager
    This class represents the layout context.

    It provides several methods to access data as well as adding and removing elements.
